Mylène Demongeot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myl%C3%A8ne_Demongeot 0 Mylène Demongeot (born Marie-Hélène Demongeot; 29 September 1935) is a French actress with a career spanning six decades. She has appeared in 72 films since 1953. Mylène_Demongeot ( born Marie-Hélène_Demongeot ; 29_September_1935 ) is a_French_actress with a_career spanning six_decades .
